<L>__{exterior bihar day (dawn, summer, mid 1980)}
<A>__{heat that has mass. that rises off the parched earth in shimmering waves. after a moment, we see what appear to be figures coming out of the haze, one by one. a family with their few belongings: hasari pal, 33, his wife, aloka, 28, and their children, daughter, amrita, 13, sons manooj and shambu, 11 and 9; hasari's mother and father. they embark toward the night, the rising sun behind them.}
